cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.IT. 

The paper is about mechanism design theory, which is a subfield of game theory. Therefore, cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses sponsored search auctions and combinatorial auctions, which are topics related to artificial intelligence and optimization, respectively. Hence, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper deals with information theory and the amount of information available to agents, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory) as a possible category.
